{
  "stem": "490.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were a lot of people from the city, who worked in different kind of works.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like when they-- they worked for building-- making bricks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the city, there were all kinds of suppliers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They worked for the Germans, making shoes-- all kinds of projects.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And these people were also kept there, while they send away the Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So after these Jews were-- the, the city was free of, of, of the Jewish population, they brought all these people which they kept in this camp.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So all of a sudden, we saw there was a lot of-- besides the workers from this, from this steel mill, they also brought the rest of the Jews, which they worked all over the city.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So let's say we were probably a few thousand young people in this camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And every, every morning, we divided-- we went to the work, to work under guard, of course, to this factory.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And everyone had his own place, where they went to work in the morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So the camp was almost-- during the day, it was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, again, I did not-- yeah, it's a matter of fact, my aunt-- this woman which, she somehow had some papers that she worked for somebody.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She did not, but she had some papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she was left, and she stayed behind in this camp, an elderly lady.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was quite sick, but somehow she managed to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And otherwise, we only had some friends which I knew from the city, young people from the yeshiva, from the school, which they also managed to stay and to, to get their paper-- working papers.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we, those were the only people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, in a place like this, we all became close friends.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
